column5: anyone bin down to the pool lately? im headed in the morning ive bin told the browns are on FIRE will let ya know tomorow night.

water was crystal clear.  hail and rain off and on all day. we got the skunk but so did most people down there today  we drifted roe, live minnows, streamers, chucked some spinners.. they were just not having it. always a great trip. appart for the climb out.
Yep, that climb out is even worse when you've been skunked, been there before. Thanks for the update.
